## Implementation Checklist
- [ ] 1. Confirm go-agent scope and current runner contract by reviewing "'`.ralph/task.md`, `.ralph/specs/04-go-agent.md`, `docs/agents/add-x-agent.md`, and existing shared-lib patterns.
